    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """A friction/failure region spanning where AI-accelerated work, sales, onboarding, and internal process all bind. The recurring AI-development pain is volume: code generated faster than humans review it ([back-pressure](narr:Narrative_AIBackPressureCodeReview), independently named by Scarlet and the customer's chief architect ([convergence](narr:Claim_AICodeVolumeBottleneck), [Scarlet's PR quote](narr:Obs_ScarletBackPressureQuote)), and the [action trap](narr:Narrative_AIActionTrap) where every response prompts another yes ([Tony](narr:Obs_TonyAITrapQuote)), plus [framing-layer over-resolution](narr:Narrative_FramingLayerDeflection). Sales friction clusters around value legibility — [compile blocks sales](narr:Claim_CompileBlocksSales), [understanding ≠ sale](narr:Obs_ScarletPurchaseTriggerQuote), [two purchase triggers](narr:Narrative_TwoPurchaseTriggers), the [activation gap](narr:Narrative_ActivationGap), [two-sided legibility](narr:Narrative_TwoSidedLegibilityProblem). Adoption friction is diagnosed as [contamination fear, not difficulty](narr:Narrative_TechnicalAdoptionFriction) ([Tony's 10 repos](narr:Obs_TechnicalChaosQuote), [privacy](narr:Obs_PrivacyConcernQuote)), plus onboarding gaps — [GitHub opacity](narr:Obs_OutsideTechBetaUserGitHubOpacityFeedback), [tool-language](narr:Obs_OutsideTechBetaUserToolLanguageFeedback), [identity grounding](narr:Narrative_IdentityOnboardingGap), [SMS trust tax](narr:Narrative_SMSContextDependentTrustTax). Internal process failures: [Notion/Backlog two-system collapse](narr:Narrative_TwoSystemDesignFailure, Jun 2026), [/start compile regression](narr:Narrative_SlashStartAbsorptionRegression, Mar), [ARB time sink](narr:Obs_ARBPainPoint1_Quote).""" ;
